text: Malcolm Sinclair is a name that may refer to *Malcolm Sinclair (Swedish nobleman) (1690–1739) whose assassination caused the Russo–Swedish War of 1741–1743 *Malcolm Sinclair (politician) (b. 1948), British politician and member of the House of Lords *Malcolm Sinclair (actor) (b. 1950), English stage and television actor and president of Equity trade union
title: Malcolm Sinclair
